
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DoX - 진단 결과</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo">DoX</h1>
            <p class="tagline">건강한 노후를 위한 스마트 진단</p>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="result-header">
                <h2>진단 결과</h2>
                <div class="patient-info">
                    <div><strong>연령:</strong> <%= age %></div>
                    <div><strong>성별:</strong> <%= gender %></div>
                    <div><strong>증상:</strong> <%= symptoms %></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="diagnosis-card">
                <div class="diagnosis-title">
                    <h3>분석된 증상: <%= matchedSymptom %></h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="diagnosis-name">
                    <%= diagnosis.diagnosis %>
                </div>
                
                <div class="medication-section">
                    <h4>권장 약물</h4>
                    <ul class="medication-list">
                        <% diagnosis.medication.forEach(med => { %>
                            <li><%= med %></li>
                        <% }) %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="advice-section">
                    <h4>건강 조언</h4>
                    <div class="advice-text">
                        <%= diagnosis.advice %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="warning-section">
                    <p><strong>주의사항:</strong> 이 진단 결과는 참고용이며, 정확한 진단을 위해서는 반드시 병원을 방문하시기 바랍니다.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">다시 진단하기</a>
                    <a href="/emergency" class="btn-emergency">응급상황 안내</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 DoX. 건강한 미래를 함께합니다.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
